rows.label: qst106012_msg0001
rows.name: I'm back, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0002
rows.name:
Welcome back, Hana, mo. I
feel a slightly more grown-up
aura from you, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0003
rows.name: Indeed, mo. Hana has become a lady, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0004
rows.name:
The outfit Kiku made is
complete, and our preparations
here are also done, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0005
rows.name:
All that's left is to wait for the
device to finish charging, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0006
rows.name: So Hana-chan will finally be reborn!

rows.label: qst106012_msg0007
rows.name: I'm getting a little nervous, mo...

rows.label: qst106012_msg0008
rows.name: So when does the modification start?

rows.label: qst106012_msg0009
rows.name:
Mo-mo-mo... It will take
another week for the
charging to complete, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0010
rows.name:
What?! Does it really take
that long to charge?

rows.label: qst106012_msg0011
rows.name:
Of course, mo! Hana's
modification requires a
massive amount of power, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0012
rows.name: It's not that simple, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0013
rows.name:
But we can't just wait a
whole week. I'll go crazy
from the anticipation.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0014
rows.name:
Isn't there a way to
speed up the charging?

rows.label: qst106012_msg0015
rows.name: Mo-mo...

rows.label: qst106012_msg0016
rows.name:
If you put materials that can become
energy into that charging device, you
can speed up the charging, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0017
rows.name:
E-Packs are the most efficient, but
other materials will work too, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0018
rows.name:
I think getting E-Packs through
the mercenary group would be
the quickest way, mo.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0019
rows.name: I see. Well then, let's give it a try.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0020
rows.name:
Hana-chan, it'll just be a
little longer, so please wait.

rows.label: qst106012_msg0021
rows.name:
Yes, mo. Everyone, I'm
counting on you, mo.
